title: SCHEDULE ENDPOINT - Use SportID, GamePk, Date and Season in an MLB request for comparison
custom_preconds:
Read in data from request against the old Stats-api (ORACLE) backend
Package results in jsonOracle object
custom_steps:
do a request to the BEAST bin-api (POSTGRES) backend
package results in jsonBeast object

compare the two objects
custom_expected: Objects should have the same content (order matching not required).
